      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;part-hugo&#34;&gt;Part Hugo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;part-upgrade&#34;&gt;Part Upgrade&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The best method to upgrade Hugo is to use the exact same method you use when you install Hugo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example, when you use homebrew to install Hugo, the please use brew to upgrade Hugo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The command of this is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;brew upgrade
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;brew upgrade hugo
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;part-config&#34;&gt;Part config&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Always the best guides:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adityatelange.github.io/hugo-PaperMod/posts/papermod/papermod-features/&#34;&gt;https://adityatelange.github.io/hugo-PaperMod/posts/papermod/papermod-features/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sometimes the config may have errors.&lt;/p&gt;
