      <guid>https://tzj2006.github.io/bugjournal/2025-01-01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;part-hugo&#34;&gt;Part Hugo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;how-to-create-a-hugo-website&#34;&gt;How to create a Hugo website&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.gohugo.org/&#34; title=&#34;hugo.org&#34;&gt;This is a good tutorial.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However, the themes may contain bugs. (The best way is to download another theme!)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Language Code Error:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Some theme use site.LanguageCode and others use site.Lang.LanguageCode&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Code Highlight Error:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Change it to &lt;code&gt;.post-content pre code { word-break: normal !important; white-space: pre !important; }&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description>
